	   _ 1.7760 German marks, up from 1.7740
	   _ 140.42 Japanese yen, up from 139.50
	   _ 1.4779 Swiss francs, up from 1.4750
	   _ 5.9565 French francs, up from 5.9479
	   _ 2.0017 Dutch guilders, up from 1.9990
