	   Editors: The following stories have moved or will move on the
European circuits of The Associated Press by 1500 GMT, unless
otherwise noted.
	   LUXEMBOURG _ The European Union on Monday banned new investments
in Serbia and froze the country's assets abroad to punish Belgrade
for staging ``widespread house-burning and indiscriminate artillery
attacks on whole villages'' in Kosovo. EU-KOSOVO.
	   DECANI-PEC ROAD IN KOSOVO, YUGOSLAVIA _ Ghastly scenes of
