<TEXT>
	   WORLD SPORTS AT 1300 GMT
 &UR; WORLD CUP:
	   PARIS _ Sepp Blatter, a last-minute candidate who waged a
globe-trotting campaign, is elected president of FIFA on Monday,
the first change at the top of soccer's world body in almost a
quarter century.
	   Slug Sports-Soccer-FIFA President. Lead has moved.
	   By Slobodan Lekic.
	   PARIS _ The FIFA presidential race, team training and
preparations for Wednesday's opening match top developments Monday
at the World Cup.
	   Slug Sports-Soccer-World Cup Roundup. Expected by 1800 GMT.
	   By Joseph White.
