	   The Thai cement, introduced by Serrex (Hong Kong) Limited was
formally launched at a city restaurant on Sunday, according to a
press release.
	   Serrex, one of the leading cement exporter to Bangladesh is
associated with TPI Polene pcl, one of the largest Thai cement
producer.
	   Imported directly from Thailand, the cement is an ordinary
portland cement produced in accordance with the American ASTM C150
Type I and BDS 232:1993.
