with massive development of Bangladesh infrastructure, is suitable
for construction work, work requiring high compressive strength,
for general concrete work such as reinforced concrete high-rise
buildings and for construction of bridges, roads, airports,
fly-overs and for various types of pre-stressed concrete products.
