Come see us for yourselves, New Yorkers told, HONGKONG STANDARD
</HEADLINE>
Come see us for yourselves, New Yorkers told, HONGKONG STANDARD &QL; 
   June 08, 1998
   HONGKONG STANDARD
   HONG KONG
   ENGLISH
   Antoine SoASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

<TEXT>
WASHINGTON, D.C. 20003 Tel: 202-547-4512 Fax: 202-546-4194
