Allocation of fund for White revolution' demanded, THE INDEPENDENT
</HEADLINE>
Allocation of fund for White revolution' demanded, THE INDEPENDENT &QL; 
   June 08, 1998
   THE INDEPENDENT
   BANGLADESH
   ENGLISH
ASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

