	   Indian Prime Minister Atal Behari Vajpayee has welcomed Prime
Minister Sheikh Hasina to visit New Delhi shortly.
	   In a letter to Sheikh Hasina Saturday, Vajpayee said it is his
pleasure to welcome her to India.
	   ``I will be happy to receive you very shortly,'' he wrote Hasina
