the Foreign Minister.
	   On May 31, Prime Minister Sheikh Hasina wrote separate letters
to Atal Behari Vajpayee and Nawaz Sharif to visit their countries
to discuss the situation arising out of nuclear tests carried out
by the two SAARC members.
	   
