	   ABUJA, Nigeria (AP) _ Nigeria's military strongman Gen. Sani
Abacha has died after suffering a heart attack, close friends of
Abacha's family said Monday.
	   In keeping with Muslim practice, a funeral will be within the
next 24 hours, said relatives who spoke to The Associated Press on
