<HEADLINE>
Celebrating admission of grads, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Celebrating admission of grads, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 06, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   MALAYSIA
   ENGLISH
   Ahmad Azlan Pa'wanASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

