<HEADLINE>
Gen. Sani Abacha: brutal even by Nigerian standards
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; RETRANSMITTING to fix slug to Nigeria sted ``Nigera'' &QL; 
 &UR; With BC-Nigeria-Abacha &QL; 

<TEXT>
	   LAGOS, Nigeria (AP) _ Even in a country long battered by
