Geoffrey Yee Lung Fook.
	   Recipients of the Panglima Setia Diraja award are Foreign
Ministry protocol chief Datuk Zainal Azman Zainal Abidin, assistant
chief of staff personnel services, Personnel Service Division,
Defence Ministry Mej Jen Baharuddin Abdul Kadir, Datuk Seri Tunku
Mahmud Tunku Besar Burhanuddin, Datuk Wong Akau and Tunku Sheilah
Tuanku Abdul Rahman.
	   There are 23 recipients of the Johan Mangku Negara award, Johan
Setia Mahkota (24), Johan Setia Diraja (15), Kesatria Mangku Negara
(261), Kesatria Setia Diraja (26), Ahli Mangku Negara (670), Pingat
Pangkuan Negara (826), Bentara Setia Diraja (41) and the Panglima
Gagah Berani and Jasa Perkasa Persekutuan (one each).
	   Among the recipients for the JMN award are the New Straits Times
Sdn Bhd assistant group editor Ahmad A. Talib, Town and Country
Planning Department director-general Datuk Zainuddin Muhammad,
Local Government Department director-general Datuk Lim Boh Ang,
