producers Harjit Singh Hullon and Normah Khalib, freelance deejay
Yasmin Yusuff and freelance newscaster Mary Anne Masilamany.
	   Other recipients are TV3's cameramen Jebat M. Roseli and
Norkamal Azedy Ahmad, assistant producer Mohd Said Abdullah Thani,
assitant engineer Hasri Abu Bakar and The Star's managing editor
Michael Aeria.
	   
