TBD-Far Eastern Economic Review, BUSINESS DAILY
</HEADLINE>
TBD-Far Eastern Economic Review, BUSINESS DAILY &QL; 
   June 08, 1998
   BUSINESS DAILY
   PHILIPPINES
   ENGLISH
