	   SHAH ALAM, Fri. - The Selangor Museum board members appointed
for 1998- 2000 have been urged to use their professionalism to
promote the museum.
	   Menteri Besar Datuk Abu Hassan Omar said they should also be
dedicated and committed in their duty as board members.
	   Abu Hassan said the museum was a showcase of Selangor's history,
culture and traditions which should be made aware to the people.
