help us to live a healthy lifestyle,'' he said when launching the
International Museum Day celebration at the State-level today.
	   He urged everyone, including government departments and
agencies, non- governmental organsations and associations to help
promote the museum by using it as a centre to hold forums,
dialogues, exhibitions, educational sessions, seminars and other
healthy activities.
	   
