<HEADLINE>
Contest to boost Commonwealth Games awareness, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Contest to boost Commonwealth Games awareness, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 06, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   MALAYSIA
   ENGLISH
ASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

<TEXT>
WASHINGTON, D.C. 20003 Tel: 202-547-4512 Fax: 202-546-4194
