<SLUG> BANANA-CAKE-THAT'S-EASY sked </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Banana cake that's easy to bake, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Banana cake that's easy to bake, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 06, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   MALAYSIA
   ENGLISH
ASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

<TEXT>
WASHINGTON, D.C. 20003 Tel: 202-547-4512 Fax: 202-546-4194
COPYRIGHT 1998 BY WORLDSOURCES, INC., A JOINT VENTURE OF FDCH, INC.
AND WORLD TIMES, INC. NO PORTION OF THE MATERIALS CONTAINED HEREIN
MAY BE USED IN ANY MEDIA WITHOUT ATTRIBUTION TO WORLDSOURCES, INC.
	   Q: I HAVE always enjoyed your column and I would appreciate
recipes for a Moist Banana Cake and a Moist Carrot Cake without any
sort of nuts in them as my daughter doesn't like cakes with nuts.
	   A: YOU can generally omit the nuts from banana or carrot cake
recipes if the amount stated is insignificant. However, you will
have to reduce baking time to turn out a moist cake.
	   Here's a great recipe for a simple banana cake which is moist
and loaded with bananas. Use very ripe bananas and mash them well.
I prefer pisang rastali for this recipe.
	   BANANA CAKE Sifted ingredients (combined): 250g self-raising
flour 1 tsp baking powder 1 tsp bicarbonate of soda 1/4 tsp salt
240g caster sugar 250g cold margarine, diced Banana Mixture
(combined) 1/3 cup milk 1 cup well-mashed ripe bananas 1 tsp
vanilla essence 2 large eggs Method Line a 23cm square cake pan
with greased baking paper.
	   Put sifted dry ingredients into bowl of a food processor
together with salt and caster sugar. Whizz for a few records to
combine mixture. Add margarine and process until mixture turns
crumbly. Beat in combined milk and banana mixture.
	   Pour into prepared pan and bake in moderately hot oven 190
degrees Celsius for 25-30 minutes or until a skewer inserted in the
centre of the cake comes out clean.
	   Cool cake in the tin for 15 minutes before turning it out onto a
wire rack to cool completely.
	   
</TEXT>
Copyright 1998 NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES all rights
reserved as distributed by WorldSources, Inc. 	   
