<HEADLINE>
AP-Pronunciation Guide (Monday)
</HEADLINE>

<TEXT>
	   News
Sani Abacha -- SAH'-nee ah-BA'-chah 
Paul Begala -- beh-GAL'-uh 
Viktor Chernomyrdin -- chehr-nuh-MEER'-din 
Eritrea -- eh-rih-TREE'-uh 
Eschede -- ESH'-eh-deh   
Lauch Faircloth -- lahk 
Michael Fortier -- FOR'-tee-ur 
Moammar Gadhafi -- MOO'-ah-mahr gah-DAH'-fee 
Rudolph Giuliani -- joo-lee-AH'-nee 
B.J. Habibie -- hah-BEE'-bee 
