	   HWANG-DBS Securities Bhd, which has set up a full-fledged
stockbroking branch office in Shah Alam, yesterday said that it
would send letters to the affected eligible clients of Omega
Securities by June 15 informing them of the detailed terms and
procedures of payment under the Reimbursement Scheme.
	   An advertisement outlining the detailed procedure will be placed
in all major newspapers on June 15 and clients of Omega are advised
to look out for these advertisements.
	   
