IPB calls on alumni to help farmers, JAKARTA POST
</HEADLINE>
IPB calls on alumni to help farmers, JAKARTA POST &QL; 
   June 08, 1998
   JAKARTA POST
   INDONESIA
   ENGLISH
ASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

