<SLUG> SOUTHERN-BANK-BHD sked </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Southern Bank Bhd, BUSINESS TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Southern Bank Bhd, BUSINESS TIMES &QL; 
   June 08, 1998
   BUSINESS TIMES
   MALAYSIA
   ENGLISH
ASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

<TEXT>
