	   Jollibee opens US store. Jollibee Foods Corp. (JFC) is set to
formally open its first Jollibee store in Daly City, Southern
California, USA on June 12, coinciding with the celebration of the
Philippines' 100th year of independence.
	   According to JFC President Tony Tan Caktiong, Jollibee's entry
into the US is one of the biggest milestones in the compay's
20-year existence.
	   Located at the heart of Daly City's business and commercial
area, the soon-to-open Jolibee store features a spacious dining
area that can accommodate close to a hundred customers, a playland,
and a drive-thru counter.
	   Currently, Jollibee is expanding its presence in countries like
Hongkong, Bruei, Indonesia, Guam, Vietnam, Malaysia, UAE, Kuwait,
Bahrain, and Saudi Arabia. It will also soon put up shop in the San
Francisco Bay Area.
	   Joy Ultra SETs Record. A total of 3,674 plates were washed with
a 250 ml.
	   bottle of New Intensified Joy Ultra in exactly six hours, one
minute, and forty seconds at the Joy-Hyatt Hotel Challenge.
	   Chief Stewart Jerome Lozada of Hyatt Regency Manila supervised
twelve dishwashers at the penthouse kitchen of the Hyatt Regency
Manila to ensure that dishes were washed according to five-star
hotel standards.
	   Punongbayan &AMP; Araullo auditors verified the number of washed
plates under the live coverage of ABS-CBN crew. According to the
auditors, the entire load of plates when stacked will rise higher
than the Hyatt Regency Hotel Manila.
	   
</TEXT>
