<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 06/08/1998 16:55:00 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
w1969 &Cx1f; wstm-
r w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  HING-YIAP-KNITTINGsked     06-08 0191
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> HING-YIAP-KNITTING sked </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Hing Yiap Knitting Industries Bhd, BUSINESS TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Hing Yiap Knitting Industries Bhd, BUSINESS TIMES &QL; 
   June 08, 1998
   BUSINESS TIMES
