<SLUG> CLEARLY-FLAWLESS sked </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Clearly flawless, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Clearly flawless, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 07, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   MALAYSIA
   ENGLISH
   R. SharminiASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

<TEXT>
WASHINGTON, D.C. 20003 Tel: 202-547-4512 Fax: 202-546-4194
COPYRIGHT 1998 BY WORLDSOURCES, INC., A JOINT VENTURE OF FDCH, INC.
AND WORLD TIMES, INC. NO PORTION OF THE MATERIALS CONTAINED HEREIN
MAY BE USED IN ANY MEDIA WITHOUT ATTRIBUTION TO WORLDSOURCES, INC.
	   MANY women, at sometime or other, have looked in the mirror and
seen the reflection of a dull, lacklustre complexion.
	   A clear luminous complexion is a symbol of beauty, yet it is
constantly under threat.
	   The sun's rays, the ageing process, fatigue and the stress of
modern living are just some factors that combine to cast a shadow
over skin.
	   Women today are more aware of the need to protect their skin so
as to preserve its beauty and radiance, ageing gracefully and
beautifully.
	   But beyond mere protection, appropriate cosmetic formulas can
now go further and have a genuine action on the clarity of the
complexion, provided they are pertinent, scientifically-tested,
developed by experts and based on in-depth knowledge of skin
metabolism.
	   Using innovative and highly specialised technologies, applied
for the first time to a cosmetic formulation developed to clarify
the skin, Christian Dior laboratories have responded with a super
formula - White Essentiel.
	   Adopting a new approach to AHAs, White Essentiel has a
combination of an AHA with a filmogenic macro-molecule that helps
stabilise it in the topmost layers of the skin. White Essentiel
works via direct action on the mechanisms of pigmentation.
	   Since its launch on May 1 in Malaysia, many local women have
reported success with glowing results after using White Essentiel
on a daily basis.
	   ``It just takes a few days of regular usage to show an
improvement in skin texture and clarity,'' says Eugenia Loh of
Christian Dior.
	   ``The ingredients in White Essentiel work indirectly on the
messages that trigger pigmentation.''
	   The success of this skin-care formula lies in Dior's commitment
towards finding the solution to creating the perfect, flawless,
clear complexion.
	   Targeting clarifying skin care as their key focus in their
research and development programme, research experts at Dior worked
on three fundamental questions that naturally arise: Why does
complexion become dull?
	   Why do dark spots appear?
	   How is it possible to go further in clarifying skin care?
	   With age, fatigue and stress, an unhealthy lifestyle and
repeated exposure of the sun's rays, the natural skin renewal
process, which occurs approximately every 28 days, is slower.
	   Repeated exposure to UV rays is a major factor in developing an
excessive number of free radicals that overstimulates tyrosinase
and triggers over production of melanin.
	   Massed in the cells, melanin then builds up in the skin,
becomingly increasingly difficult to eliminate and leading to the
formation of dark spots or freckles.
	   Dior laboratories have demonstrated in laboratory tests that the
application of a Vitamin C derivative to a sample of isolated skin
exposed to UV rays, reduces the level of thymine dimers
(photo-products of cell degeneration), showing a protective effect
of the vitamin against the damage of UV rays.
	   The global action of Vitamin C on tyrosinase is combined with
that of Licorice Extract and these two agents ensure a reinforced
action on excessive pigmentation.
	   The oxidising stress caused by free radicals is a factor in the
over- production of melanin but by enriching a clarifying formula
with a cell protection agent, it is possible to optimise its
effectiveness.
	   White Essentiel offers a dual skin-lightening performance and
represents an essential contribution to the progress of
cosmetology. For the first time, two clarifying technologies are
combined for increased effectiveness on skin clarity.
	   Because of their exfoliating action, AHAs are capable of
breaking the microscopic bonds, which link dead cells together.
Once the cells are separated from each other, they can be
eliminated more easily.
	   The addition of malic acid and a sweet almond protein help
stabilise the AHA in the top layer of skin and prevents it from
migrating down to the deeper layers. This ensures a surface
exfoliating action which is perfectly controlled, continuous and
ultra-gentle.
	   Skin is simulated and can renew itself more quickly; dead cells
clustered on the surface of the skin and charged with melanin are
eliminated.
	   Roughness is diminished, the complexion visibly smoothened and
brightened - all so gently. Thanks to a unique synergy of actions
in White Essentiel, the formation of melanin is limited from the
start. This results in an even clearer, more even flawless
complexion.
	   Smoothed, refined, renewed, the complexion becomes fresher,
brighter and more luminous. The dull film is gently smoothed away.
Dark spots and freckles appear less visible, the skin is more even,
its clarity spectacularly enhanced. Used day after day, White
Essentiel revives the radiance and translucent quality of the skin.
	   This formula is of a fresh delicate texture - an ultra fluid,
transparent and absolutely non-greasy essence. It is absorbed by
the skin in a few seconds.
	   The essential skin-brightening ritual for the face and neck, it
should be used all year round, morning and night, before any other
skin care product.
	   Presented in a pearly white bottle with curved, feminine lines,
White Essentiel's precious essence is dispensed by a dropper system
for ultra- precise dosage. Just two or three drops are enough for
the whole face.
	   The opaque finish of the bottle protects all the properties and
effectiveness of the formula's active ingredients.
	   It is priced at RM150 for the 30ml bottle (RM158 in Sabah,
Sarawak) and RM220 for the 50ml (RM231 in Sabah, Sarawak).
	   
</TEXT>
