 &UR; WORLD CUP:
	   PARIS _ Brazil is gunning for its fifth World Cup title.
Scotland is trying to get past the first round at the eighth
attempt. Wednesday's opening game of the biggest World Cup ever
brings together the championship's most successful nation against
the one with the worst record in the finals. It's that kind of
World Cup.
