<HEADLINE>
U.S. Open Qualifying Scores
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; Eds: The USGA did not make late qualifying results available &QL; 

<TEXT>
	   FAR HILLS, New Jersey (AP) _ Scores Monday from sectional
qualifying for the 1998 U.S. Open, to be played June 18-21 at the
Olympic Club in San Francisco (a-amateur):
 &UR; At Orlando, Florida &QC; 
 &UR; The Bay Hill Club &QC; 
Grant Waite                  &Cx1f; 71-66_137
Brett Wetterich              &Cx1f; 69-72_141
